Comment: 50,0:00:16.00,0:00:16.04,Default,chptr,0,0,0,,Cold Open
Comment: 50,0:00:54.03,0:00:54.08,Default,chptr,0,0,0,opsync,OP
Comment: 50,0:02:25.00,0:02:25.04,Default,chptr,0,0,0,,Part A
Comment: 50,0:10:32.03,0:10:32.07,Default,chptr,0,0,0,,Part B
Comment: 50,0:22:23.03,0:22:23.07,Default,chptr,0,0,0,edsync,ED
Comment: 50,0:23:53.04,0:23:53.08,Default,chptr,0,0,0,,Preview
Dialogue: 50,0:02:37.47,0:02:39.43,Default,Fuu,0,0,0,,Morning, big sis.
Dialogue: 50,0:02:39.43,0:02:40.60,Default,Rui,0,0,0,,Good morning, Fuu.
Dialogue: 50,0:02:40.60,0:02:42.31,Default,Fuu,0,0,0,,I had a weird dream.
Dialogue: 50,0:02:42.31,0:02:43.48,Default,Rui,0,0,0,,I see.{そうなの}
Dialogue: 50,0:02:50.36,0:02:53.15,Default,Mom,0,0,0,,I should check up on the kids soon.
Dialogue: 50,0:02:53.15,0:02:54.99,Default,Dad,0,0,0,,Sounds good.
Dialogue: 50,0:03:02.66,0:03:04.33,Default,Mom,0,0,0,,You're still not dressed?
Dialogue: 50,0:03:04.33,0:03:06.17,Default,Rui,0,0,0,,Good morning, Mom!
Dialogue: 50,0:03:06.54,0:03:09.04,Default,Mom,0,0,0,,At least you can give a first-class greeting.
Dialogue: 50,0:03:09.50,0:03:10.96,Default,Rui,0,0,0,,Thank you for breakfast.
Dialogue: 50,0:03:10.96,0:03:13.38,Default,Mom,0,0,0,,You're leaving already, Rui?
Dialogue: 50,0:03:13.38,0:03:14.84,Default,Rui,0,0,0,,I have classroom duties.
Dialogue: 50,0:03:15.68,0:03:18.14,Default,Mom,0,0,0,,It's hot out, so stay safe, okay?
Dialogue: 50,0:03:18.59,0:03:20.56,Default,Rui,0,0,0,,I will.
Dialogue: 50,0:03:23.22,0:03:24.56,Default,Rui,0,0,0,,Goodbye, Mom.
Dialogue: 50,0:03:24.56,0:03:26.14,Default,Mom,0,0,0,,Take care.
Dialogue: 50,0:03:27.60,0:03:29.52,Default,Mom,0,0,0,,Fuu, hurry up and get to school!
Dialogue: 50,0:03:29.52,0:03:30.94,Default,Fuu,0,0,0,,I know...
Dialogue: 50,0:03:36.11,0:03:37.95,Default,Fuu,0,0,0,,Bye, Mom!
Dialogue: 50,0:03:47.75,0:03:49.13,Default,Fuu,0,0,0,,Big sis!
Dialogue: 50,0:03:49.92,0:03:53.17,Default,Fuu,0,0,0,,Wanna go to the pool with me\Nover summer break?
Dialogue: 50,0:03:57.18,0:03:58.30,Default,Fuu,0,0,0,,Is that a no?
Dialogue: 50,0:03:59.18,0:04:02.81,Default,Rui,0,0,0,,I need to use my break\Nto catch up on my studies.
Dialogue: 50,0:04:03.47,0:04:04.81,Default,Fuu,0,0,0,,Studying over your break?
Dialogue: 50,0:04:05.43,0:04:07.06,Default,Fuu,0,0,0,,You're such a hard worker.
Dialogue: 50,0:04:07.64,0:04:08.48,Default,Rui,0,0,0,,See you later.
Dialogue: 50,0:04:08.48,0:04:09.27,Default,Fuu,0,0,0,,Later!
Dialogue: 50,0:04:15.57,0:04:18.20,Default,Fuu,0,0,0,,Darn, I really wanted to\Ngo to the pool with her...
Dialogue: 50,0:04:19.49,0:04:20.57,Default,Fuu,0,0,0,,S-Sorry!
Dialogue: 50,0:04:20.99,0:04:22.28,Default,Shota,0,0,0,,Hey, Fuu.
Dialogue: 50,0:04:22.28,0:04:23.58,Default,Fuu,0,0,0,,Oh, Sho-chan!
Dialogue: 50,0:04:24.33,0:04:25.58,Default,Shota,0,0,0,,You never change, huh?
Dialogue: 50,0:04:25.58,0:04:26.95,Default,Fuu,0,0,0,,Good morning!
Dialogue: 50,0:04:26.95,0:04:27.75,Default,Shota,0,0,0,,Mornin'.
Dialogue: 50,0:04:28.25,0:04:29.71,Default,Shota,0,0,0,,How's Rui doing?
Dialogue: 50,0:04:29.71,0:04:31.54,Default,Fuu,0,0,0,,She's great!
Dialogue: 50,0:04:31.54,0:04:33.96,Default,Shota,0,0,0,,Ahh... good to hear.
Dialogue: 50,0:04:33.96,0:04:36.63,Default,Fuu,0,0,0,,You wanna play with me\Nover summer break?
Dialogue: 50,0:04:36.63,0:04:38.72,Default,Fuu,0,0,0,,You can teach me basketball!
Dialogue: 50,0:04:38.72,0:04:40.18,Default,Shota,0,0,0,,Whoa there.
Dialogue: 50,0:04:41.43,0:04:43.35,Default,Shota,0,0,0,,No can do. My club's got a game.
Dialogue: 50,0:04:43.35,0:04:44.97,Default,Fuu,0,0,0,,Aww...
Dialogue: 50,0:04:44.97,0:04:45.81,Default,Shota,0,0,0,,See ya.
Dialogue: 50,0:04:52.15,0:04:57.57,Default,Fuu,0,0,0,,Aw, man. No one has any time\Nto play with me.
Dialogue: 50,0:04:57.57,0:04:59.65,Default,Fuu,0,0,0,,It wasn't always this way...
Dialogue: 50,0:05:00.95,0:05:04.66,Default,Fuu,0,0,0,,{\an8\i1}Big sis would always sing for me.
Dialogue: 50,0:05:00.03,0:05:04.66,Default,Rui,0,0,0,,{\i1}I made a wish to the stars
Dialogue: 50,0:05:04.66,0:05:09.46,Default,Rui,0,0,0,,{\i1}Up in the twinkling sky
Dialogue: 50,0:05:09.46,0:05:13.17,Default,Rui,0,0,0,,{\i1}Beyond the fluffy clouds
Dialogue: 50,0:05:17.26,0:05:18.38,Default,Mom,0,0,0,,Rui?!
Dialogue: 50,0:05:21.22,0:05:23.64,Default,Fuu,0,0,0,,{\i1}But then she got sick\Nand went to the hospital,
Dialogue: 50,0:05:24.18,0:05:25.97,Default,Fuu,0,0,0,,{\i1}and lost her spirit.
Dialogue: 50,0:05:27.22,0:05:30.14,Default,Fuu,0,0,0,,{\an8\i1}I think she's all healed up now,\Nbut still...
Dialogue: 50,0:05:32.40,0:05:35.06,Default,Fuu,0,0,0,,Where did everyone go?
Dialogue: 50,0:05:35.90,0:05:37.78,Default,Fuu,0,0,0,,I'm so lonely...
Dialogue: 50,0:05:39.99,0:05:43.03,Default,Fuu,0,0,0,,Just when summer break\Nis around the corner...
Dialogue: 50,0:05:48.20,0:05:49.37,Default,Iroha,0,0,0,,Fuu-chan!
Dialogue: 50,0:05:49.37,0:05:51.16,Default,Hayato,0,0,0,,Hurry up, or we'll be late.
Dialogue: 50,0:05:51.16,0:05:52.87,Default,Fuu,0,0,0,,M-Morning!
Dialogue: 50,0:05:56.54,0:06:01.42,Default,Teacher,0,0,0,,As you'll remember from our observation,\Ntadpoles hatch from frog eggs.
Dialogue: 50,0:06:01.42,0:06:05.05,Default,Teacher,0,0,0,,So how do you think that medaka fish are born?
Dialogue: 50,0:06:05.05,0:06:07.76,Default,Teacher,0,0,0,,They also hatch from eggs.
Dialogue: 50,0:06:07.76,0:06:10.56,Default,Teacher,0,0,0,,We're going to observe medaka in a tank...
Dialogue: 50,0:06:11.68,0:06:13.27,Default,Fuu,0,0,0,,{\i1}Is that a spaceship?
Dialogue: 50,0:06:13.90,0:06:19.15,Default,Fuu,0,0,0,,{\i1}Are the aliens here to abduct me\Nfrom my boredom?
Dialogue: 50,0:06:19.78,0:06:21.74,Default,Fuu,0,0,0,,{\i1}There's no way.
Dialogue: 50,0:06:32.08,0:06:33.71,Default,Fuu,0,0,0,,{\i1}It really is a spaceship!
Dialogue: 50,0:06:33.71,0:06:35.88,Default,Fuu,0,0,0,,{\i1}Please, come over here!
Dialogue: 50,0:06:38.25,0:06:39.67,Default,Fuu,0,0,0,,Wait up!
Dialogue: 50,0:06:40.17,0:06:41.51,Default,Teacher,0,0,0,,Nonoyama-san?
Dialogue: 50,0:06:41.51,0:06:43.01,Default,Teacher,0,0,0,,Nonoyama-san!
Dialogue: 50,0:06:43.01,0:06:45.09,Default,Fuu,0,0,0,,Sensei, look outside!
Dialogue: 50,0:06:46.76,0:06:48.47,Default,Teacher,0,0,0,,There's nothing there.
Dialogue: 50,0:06:48.76,0:06:52.18,Default,Teacher,0,0,0,,A spaceship just passed by, I swear!
Dialogue: 50,0:06:52.18,0:06:53.35,Default,Iroha,0,0,0,,Did you see it?
Dialogue: 50,0:06:53.35,0:06:55.52,Default,Hayato,0,0,0,,Nope. Didn't see nothing.
Dialogue: 50,0:06:55.81,0:06:58.52,Default,Teacher,0,0,0,,Nonoyama-san, please take your seat.
Dialogue: 50,0:06:59.40,0:07:00.65,Default,Fuu,0,0,0,,Sorry.
Dialogue: 50,0:07:00.65,0:07:02.69,Default,Teacher,0,0,0,,Let's resume the lesson.
Dialogue: 50,0:07:04.11,0:07:06.70,Default,Classmate,0,0,0,,Hey, wanna go do karaoke after this?
Dialogue: 50,0:07:06.70,0:07:07.95,Default,Mizuka,0,0,0,,Sure, I'd love to!
Dialogue: 50,0:07:07.95,0:07:09.45,Default,Momo,0,0,0,,Same place?
Dialogue: 50,0:07:09.45,0:07:10.28,Default,Mizuka,0,0,0,,Yeah!
Dialogue: 50,0:07:10.87,0:07:12.41,Default,Mizuka,0,0,0,,Let's ask Rui-chan.
Dialogue: 50,0:07:12.41,0:07:12.95,Default,Momo,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 50,0:07:14.71,0:07:16.37,Default,Momo,0,0,0,,Wanna join us, Nonoyama-san?
Dialogue: 50,0:07:17.00,0:07:19.71,Default,Mizuka,0,0,0,,Rui-chan, we're doing karaoke! You in?
Dialogue: 50,0:07:20.46,0:07:23.21,Default,Rui,0,0,0,,Sorry, I don't really sing.
Dialogue: 50,0:07:23.55,0:07:24.51,Default,Mizuka,0,0,0,,Darn.
Dialogue: 50,0:07:24.51,0:07:28.64,Default,Momo,0,0,0,,I see. I forgot you don't\Nlike noisy places.
Dialogue: 50,0:07:29.68,0:07:31.22,Default,Mizuka,0,0,0,,We'll hang out some other time.
Dialogue: 50,0:07:31.22,0:07:32.06,Default,Rui,0,0,0,,Sorry again.
Dialogue: 50,0:07:32.06,0:07:33.31,Default,Momo,0,0,0,,See you tomorrow!
Dialogue: 50,0:07:33.31,0:07:34.60,Default,Rui,0,0,0,,See you tomorrow.
Dialogue: 50,0:07:40.48,0:07:42.23,Default,Iroha,0,0,0,,What's the matter, Fuu-chan?
Dialogue: 50,0:07:42.23,0:07:44.94,Default,Fuu,0,0,0,,I swear, I really saw one.
Dialogue: 50,0:07:44.94,0:07:46.36,Default,Hayato,0,0,0,,You mean the spaceship?
Dialogue: 50,0:07:46.36,0:07:48.57,Default,Iroha,0,0,0,,Are you still looking for it?
Dialogue: 50,0:07:48.57,0:07:53.37,Default,Fuu,0,0,0,,I mean, that thing was huge!\NHow did no one else see it?
Dialogue: 50,0:07:53.37,0:07:55.66,Default,Fuu,0,0,0,,Like, it was {\i1}this{\i0} big!
Dialogue: 50,0:07:55.66,0:07:58.87,Default,Fuu,0,0,0,,And it went right up past the window!
Dialogue: 50,0:07:59.79,0:08:01.21,Default,Hayato,0,0,0,,Are you sure?
Dialogue: 50,0:08:01.21,0:08:02.63,Default,Iroha,0,0,0,,We didn't see it.
Dialogue: 50,0:08:02.63,0:08:05.67,Default,Fuu,0,0,0,,How? It flew right past us—
Dialogue: 50,0:08:11.89,0:08:13.39,Default,Fuu,0,0,0,,Those are funny-looking cats.
Dialogue: 50,0:08:13.39,0:08:14.72,Default,Uguisu,0,0,0,,What was that for?
Dialogue: 50,0:08:14.72,0:08:16.10,Default,Azuki,0,0,0,,Take it easy.
Dialogue: 50,0:08:18.52,0:08:20.65,Default,Dad,0,0,0,,I'll handle the deliveries tomorrow.
Dialogue: 50,0:08:20.65,0:08:22.15,Default,Mom,0,0,0,,Are you sure?
Dialogue: 50,0:08:22.15,0:08:23.48,Default,Dad,0,0,0,,Of course. It's hot out.
Dialogue: 50,0:08:23.48,0:08:24.73,Default,Mom,0,0,0,,Aww, you.
Dialogue: 50,0:08:24.73,0:08:25.99,Default,Rui,0,0,0,,Thank you for dinner.
Dialogue: 50,0:08:28.49,0:08:30.20,Default,Fuu,0,0,0,,Hey, big sis!
Dialogue: 50,0:08:30.66,0:08:33.03,Default,Fuu,0,0,0,,Anything fun happen at school?
Dialogue: 50,0:08:33.03,0:08:36.95,Default,Fuu,0,0,0,,I have a super big story!
Dialogue: 50,0:08:36.95,0:08:38.16,Default,Rui,0,0,0,,Today, huh?
Dialogue: 50,0:08:38.66,0:08:40.12,Default,Rui,0,0,0,,Well, my homeroom teacher...
Dialogue: 50,0:08:40.12,0:08:41.08,Default,Fuu,0,0,0,,Yeah?
Dialogue: 50,0:08:41.63,0:08:43.13,Default,Rui,0,0,0,,...said it was his birthday today.
Dialogue: 50,0:08:43.13,0:08:45.00,Default,Fuu,0,0,0,,Ooh! Go on!
Dialogue: 50,0:08:45.76,0:08:47.59,Default,Rui,0,0,0,,That's about it, I think.
Dialogue: 50,0:08:47.59,0:08:48.88,Default,Fuu,0,0,0,,Oh, okay.
Dialogue: 50,0:08:49.47,0:08:51.68,Default,Rui,0,0,0,,What's your "super big story," Fuu?
Dialogue: 50,0:08:53.26,0:08:55.31,Default,Fuu,0,0,0,,It's nothing, actually.
Dialogue: 50,0:08:55.31,0:08:56.68,Default,Rui,0,0,0,,I see.{そうなの}
Dialogue: 50,0:08:57.14,0:08:58.93,Default,Rui,0,0,0,,I'm going to go take a bath.
Dialogue: 50,0:08:58.93,0:09:00.19,Default,Fuu,0,0,0,,Okay!
Dialogue: 50,0:09:00.85,0:09:02.65,Default,Mom,0,0,0,,Why don't you go with her?
Dialogue: 50,0:09:03.40,0:09:05.23,Default,Fuu,0,0,0,,I'm good.
Dialogue: 50,0:09:05.69,0:09:08.36,Default,Dad,0,0,0,,Didn't they usually bathe together?
Dialogue: 50,0:09:08.36,0:09:09.86,Default,Mom,0,0,0,,Guess she's growing up.
Dialogue: 50,0:09:09.86,0:09:11.99,Default,Fuu,0,0,0,,Am not...
Dialogue: 50,0:09:27.25,0:09:29.30,Default,Fuu,0,0,0,,Slow down, big sis!
Dialogue: 50,0:10:02.46,0:10:06.71,Default,Rui,0,0,0,,{\i1}I made a wish to the stars
Dialogue: 50,0:10:13.47,0:10:14.93,Default,Fuu,0,0,0,,It was a dream...
Dialogue: 50,0:10:18.97,0:10:21.64,Default,Fuu,0,0,0,,{\i1}I made a wish to...
Dialogue: 50,0:10:23.14,0:10:26.73,Default,Fuu,0,0,0,,I want to hear big sis sing again...
Dialogue: 50,0:10:27.77,0:10:28.77,Default,Mom,0,0,0,,Fuu!
Dialogue: 50,0:10:29.69,0:10:31.40,Default,Fuu,0,0,0,,I'm up!
Dialogue: 50,0:10:33.07,0:10:36.03,Default,Teacher,0,0,0,,2 meters of red ribbon costs ¥32.
Dialogue: 50,0:10:36.49,0:10:40.45,Default,Teacher,0,0,0,,1.6 meters of blue ribbon also costs ¥32.
Dialogue: 50,0:10:40.95,0:10:48.00,Default,Teacher,0,0,0,,What is the price of 1 meter each\Nof red and blue ribbon?
Dialogue: 50,0:10:50.30,0:10:52.17,Default,Fuu,0,0,0,,No sign of it.
Dialogue: 50,0:10:57.43,0:11:01.35,Default,Teacher,0,0,0,,Let's start with the red ribbon.
Dialogue: 50,0:11:01.35,0:11:06.98,Default,Teacher,0,0,0,,To get the price of 1 meter,\Nyou divide the cost by the length.
Dialogue: 50,0:11:06.98,0:11:11.11,Default,Fuu,0,0,0,,{\i1}If I run into it again,\Nmaybe things will change.
Dialogue: 50,0:11:11.69,0:11:13.49,Default,Iroha,0,0,0,,You going anywhere for summer break?
Dialogue: 50,0:11:13.49,0:11:15.82,Default,Hayato,0,0,0,,I'm going to my grandma's house\Nby the beach!
Dialogue: 50,0:11:15.82,0:11:17.49,Default,Iroha,0,0,0,,Aw, that sounds nice!
Dialogue: 50,0:11:17.49,0:11:18.20,Default,Hayato,0,0,0,,What about you?
Dialogue: 50,0:11:18.20,0:11:20.12,Default,Iroha,0,0,0,,I dunno... maybe the beach too!
Dialogue: 50,0:11:21.20,0:11:21.83,Default,Hayato,0,0,0,,Later!
Dialogue: 50,0:11:21.83,0:11:23.16,Default,Iroha,0,0,0,,See you tomorrow!
Dialogue: 50,0:11:23.16,0:11:25.37,Default,Fuu,0,0,0,,Oh, uh, bye!
Dialogue: 50,0:11:30.50,0:11:33.55,Default,Fuu,0,0,0,,{\i1}Please, spaceship, come here again!
Dialogue: 50,0:11:33.55,0:11:34.59,Default,Fuu,0,0,0,,{\i1}I'm begging you!
Dialogue: 50,0:11:47.52,0:11:48.60,Default,Fuu,0,0,0,,It's back!
Dialogue: 50,0:11:55.03,0:11:56.57,Default,Fuu,0,0,0,,Wait up!
Dialogue: 50,0:12:18.38,0:12:20.68,Default,Meeter,0,0,0,,The view here is just wonderful.
Dialogue: 50,0:12:21.01,0:12:22.51,Default,Uguisu,0,0,0,,It's so hot...
Dialogue: 50,0:12:22.51,0:12:24.18,Default,Azuki,0,0,0,,They call this "summer!"
Dialogue: 50,0:12:24.85,0:12:27.43,Default,Meeter,0,0,0,,Take a look. The sun is about to set.
Dialogue: 50,0:12:27.43,0:12:28.48,Default,Uguisu,0,0,0,,Let's see here.
Dialogue: 50,0:12:28.48,0:12:29.19,Default,Azuki,0,0,0,,Hup.
Dialogue: 50,0:12:29.98,0:12:31.48,Default,Azuki,0,0,0,,How beautiful!
Dialogue: 50,0:12:31.48,0:12:32.73,Default,Uguisu,0,0,0,,It's so bright.
Dialogue: 50,0:12:32.73,0:12:33.44,Default,Azuki,0,0,0,,Oh?
Dialogue: 50,0:12:36.32,0:12:39.07,Default,Azuki,0,0,0,,There's a child chasing after us.
Dialogue: 50,0:12:37.03,0:12:39.07,Default,Fuu,0,0,0,,{\an8}Please, wait for me!
Dialogue: 50,0:12:39.07,0:12:40.45,Default,Azuki,0,0,0,,It's the one from yesterday.
Dialogue: 50,0:12:40.45,0:12:42.32,Default,Uguisu,0,0,0,,That little brat!
Dialogue: 50,0:12:42.66,0:12:46.54,Default,Meeter,0,0,0,,Strange. Humans shouldn't be able\Nto see this ship.
Dialogue: 50,0:12:51.00,0:12:52.92,Default,Fuu,0,0,0,,Wait for me!
Dialogue: 50,0:12:53.63,0:12:54.46,Default,Meeter,0,0,0,,What's going on?
Dialogue: 50,0:12:58.72,0:12:59.72,Default,Fuu,0,0,0,,Please stop!
Dialogue: 50,0:13:09.35,0:13:10.60,Default,Fuu,0,0,0,,I'm almost there...
Dialogue: 50,0:13:19.82,0:13:20.70,Default,Meeter,0,0,0,,Oh no!
Dialogue: 50,0:13:58.82,0:14:00.28,Default,Fuu,0,0,0,,Owie...
Dialogue: 50,0:14:05.41,0:14:07.49,Default,Meeter,0,0,0,,That was a close call.
Dialogue: 50,0:14:10.29,0:14:11.75,Default,Fuu,0,0,0,,Those cats from yesterday!
Dialogue: 50,0:14:11.75,0:14:13.12,Default,Uguisu,0,0,0,,Who are you?
Dialogue: 50,0:14:13.12,0:14:14.46,Default,Azuki,0,0,0,,Are you okay?
Dialogue: 50,0:14:14.46,0:14:15.88,Default,Fuu,0,0,0,,They're talking!
Dialogue: 50,0:14:16.67,0:14:17.63,Default,Azuki,0,0,0,,Yes we are.
Dialogue: 50,0:14:20.34,0:14:24.51,Default,Fuu,0,0,0,,I actually made it\Non the spaceship...
Dialogue: 50,0:14:24.51,0:14:25.72,Default,Meeter,0,0,0,,Ehem.
Dialogue: 50,0:14:26.35,0:14:27.97,Default,Meeter,0,0,0,,Who would you be?
Dialogue: 50,0:14:27.97,0:14:30.81,Default,Fuu,0,0,0,,I'm Nonoyama Fuu.
Dialogue: 50,0:14:30.81,0:14:34.23,Default,Fuu,0,0,0,,Is this really a spaceship?
Dialogue: 50,0:14:34.69,0:14:36.36,Default,Meeter,0,0,0,,It's a magic ship.
Dialogue: 50,0:14:36.36,0:14:41.07,Default,Meeter,0,0,0,,I am Meeter. I come from the magical land Felix Star.
Dialogue: 50,0:14:41.07,0:14:42.90,Default,Meeter,0,0,0,,We're visiting this planet—
Dialogue: 50,0:14:42.90,0:14:44.11,Default,Fuu,0,0,0,,Um, I...
Dialogue: 50,0:14:44.66,0:14:48.99,Default,Fuu,0,0,0,,I had to make it onto this ship, because...
Dialogue: 50,0:14:50.24,0:14:53.21,Default,Fuu,0,0,0,,the way things are going,\Nbig sis, Sho-chan,
Dialogue: 50,0:14:53.21,0:14:56.50,Default,Fuu,0,0,0,,and everyone else is gonna grow up\Nand move on,
Dialogue: 50,0:14:57.17,0:14:59.75,Default,Fuu,0,0,0,,and leave me behind...
Dialogue: 50,0:15:03.67,0:15:07.14,Default,Fuu,0,0,0,,I just want big sis to smile more,
Dialogue: 50,0:15:08.35,0:15:10.85,Default,Fuu,0,0,0,,but I don't know how to help her.
Dialogue: 50,0:15:11.47,0:15:12.64,Default,Fuu,0,0,0,,So...
Dialogue: 50,0:15:19.61,0:15:22.44,Default,Meeter,0,0,0,,You want things to change, do you?
Dialogue: 50,0:15:24.15,0:15:27.95,Default,Meeter,0,0,0,,If you have strong feelings,\Nyou can cast magic.
Dialogue: 50,0:15:29.12,0:15:31.20,Default,Meeter,0,0,0,,Want to give it a try?
Dialogue: 50,0:15:33.79,0:15:34.54,Default,Fuu,0,0,0,,Yes!
Dialogue: 50,0:15:47.01,0:15:48.05,Default,Fuu,0,0,0,,So cute...
Dialogue: 50,0:15:48.76,0:15:52.56,Default,Meeter,0,0,0,,This is a Glass Heart,\Nthe source of your magic.
Dialogue: 50,0:15:53.14,0:15:56.89,Default,Meeter,0,0,0,,Humans can only cast magic\Nfor one year.
Dialogue: 50,0:15:56.89,0:16:02.07,Default,Meeter,0,0,0,,And you cannot let any other humans\Nfind out about your magic.
Dialogue: 50,0:16:02.44,0:16:04.86,Default,Fuu,0,0,0,,Not even my mom and dad?
Dialogue: 50,0:16:06.57,0:16:07.95,Default,Fuu,0,0,0,,Or my sister...?
Dialogue: 50,0:16:08.28,0:16:09.45,Default,Meeter,0,0,0,,No one.
Dialogue: 50,0:16:11.83,0:16:16.71,Default,Meeter,0,0,0,,So long as you follow the rules,\Nyou can make something wonderful of your magic.
Dialogue: 50,0:16:16.71,0:16:20.96,Default,Meeter,0,0,0,,Now I would like to see your wish.
Dialogue: 50,0:16:21.71,0:16:23.46,Default,Fuu,0,0,0,,How do I use it?
Dialogue: 50,0:16:24.21,0:16:27.47,Default,Meeter,0,0,0,,Give it a tap and say "litto."
Dialogue: 50,0:16:29.09,0:16:30.26,Default,Fuu,0,0,0,,Litto!
Dialogue: 50,0:16:38.89,0:16:40.81,Default,Fuu,0,0,0,,A magic wand?
Dialogue: 50,0:16:40.81,0:16:43.98,Default,Meeter,0,0,0,,Now use the wand\Nand chant the magic words.
Dialogue: 50,0:16:44.73,0:16:46.53,Default,Meeter,0,0,0,,Those words are up to you.
Dialogue: 50,0:16:47.19,0:16:48.49,Default,Meeter,0,0,0,,Give it a go.
Dialogue: 50,0:16:48.49,0:16:49.24,Default,Fuu,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 50,0:16:59.08,0:17:01.00,Default,Fuu,0,0,0,,Lililula palilula!
Dialogue: 50,0:17:03.63,0:17:06.13,Default,Fuu,0,0,0,,Pam pam power!
Dialogue: 50,0:17:45.21,0:17:47.09,Default,Fuu,0,0,0,,I'm all tall now!
Dialogue: 50,0:17:47.63,0:17:50.51,Default,Meeter,0,0,0,,You transformed into your ideal self!
Dialogue: 50,0:17:50.51,0:17:52.01,Default,Azuki,0,0,0,,You look great!
Dialogue: 50,0:17:52.01,0:17:55.85,Default,Meeter,0,0,0,,You can use that wand\Nto cast any kind of spell.
Dialogue: 50,0:17:57.18,0:17:58.60,Default,Fuu,0,0,0,,Any kind, you say?
Dialogue: 50,0:17:59.06,0:18:01.35,Default,Meeter,0,0,0,,As long as you truly wish for it.
Dialogue: 50,0:18:10.03,0:18:12.40,Default,Fuu,0,0,0,,That spaceship sure stands out.
Dialogue: 50,0:18:12.78,0:18:15.20,Default,Azuki,0,0,0,,Other humans can't see it!
Dialogue: 50,0:18:15.20,0:18:16.41,Default,Fuu,0,0,0,,Oh, I see.
Dialogue: 50,0:18:16.41,0:18:19.16,Default,Fuu,0,0,0,,What kind of spell should I cast?
Dialogue: 50,0:18:19.75,0:18:23.67,Default,Fuu,0,0,0,,I think it should be something\Nthat everyone will enjoy!
Dialogue: 50,0:18:24.46,0:18:26.21,Default,Fuu,0,0,0,,Lililula palilula,
Dialogue: 50,0:18:26.21,0:18:31.30,Default,Fuu,0,0,0,,fill the sky with great big fireworks!
Dialogue: 50,0:18:48.07,0:18:49.07,Default,Shota,0,0,0,,What the?
Dialogue: 50,0:18:52.40,0:18:54.86,Default,Mom,0,0,0,,Is there a fireworks show going on?
Dialogue: 50,0:18:54.86,0:18:56.82,Default,Dad,0,0,0,,Haven't heard of any.
Dialogue: 50,0:18:57.82,0:19:01.08,Default,Dad,0,0,0,,Hey, Rui! Look outside!
Dialogue: 50,0:19:01.08,0:19:02.45,Default,Dad,0,0,0,,You'll be amazed!
Dialogue: 50,0:19:03.75,0:19:04.96,Default,Rui,0,0,0,,What is it?
Dialogue: 50,0:19:13.88,0:19:15.09,Default,Rui,0,0,0,,It's beautiful...
Dialogue: 50,0:19:26.48,0:19:28.27,Default,Fuu,0,0,0,,The spell ended.
Dialogue: 50,0:19:28.27,0:19:29.48,Default,Azuki,0,0,0,,That was great.
Dialogue: 50,0:19:29.48,0:19:30.98,Default,Uguisu,0,0,0,,Not bad.
Dialogue: 50,0:19:30.98,0:19:32.28,Default,Meeter,0,0,0,,Fantastic job.
Dialogue: 50,0:19:33.44,0:19:37.32,Default,Meeter,0,0,0,,Well done for your first spell.\NIt was a beautiful display.
Dialogue: 50,0:19:37.32,0:19:38.03,Default,Fuu,0,0,0,,You think so?
Dialogue: 50,0:19:38.49,0:19:39.66,Default,Meeter,0,0,0,,I do.
Dialogue: 50,0:19:39.66,0:19:42.04,Default,Meeter,0,0,0,,I'd better be on my way now.
Dialogue: 50,0:19:42.70,0:19:45.83,Default,Meeter,0,0,0,,I'll leave those two with you\Nin case anything happens.
Dialogue: 50,0:19:45.37,0:19:46.21,Default,Uguisu,0,0,0,,{\an8}Hey!
Dialogue: 50,0:19:45.83,0:19:48.38,Default,Meeter,0,0,0,,If you have any questions, just ask them.
Dialogue: 50,0:19:48.38,0:19:50.04,Default,Azuki,0,0,0,,We're happy to help.
Dialogue: 50,0:19:50.46,0:19:52.09,Default,Fuu,0,0,0,,So you're leaving already?
Dialogue: 50,0:19:52.09,0:19:55.72,Default,Meeter,0,0,0,,No matter what, you must keep\Nyour magic a secret from other humans.
Dialogue: 50,0:19:56.05,0:19:57.13,Default,Meeter,0,0,0,,Farewell.
Dialogue: 50,0:19:57.76,0:20:02.39,Default,Meeter,0,0,0,,We shall meet again in one year's time\Nat the Festival of Magic.
Dialogue: 50,0:20:10.73,0:20:12.90,Default,Fuu,0,0,0,,The test of all magic?
Dialogue: 50,0:20:14.23,0:20:16.49,Default,Fuu,0,0,0,,It's so dark! I gotta get home!
Dialogue: 50,0:20:16.49,0:20:18.32,Default,Fuu,0,0,0,,How do I turn back?
Dialogue: 50,0:20:18.32,0:20:20.91,Default,Azuki,0,0,0,,Just say "tohri!"
Dialogue: 50,0:20:21.24,0:20:22.37,Default,Fuu,0,0,0,,Tohri!
Dialogue: 50,0:20:29.83,0:20:33.13,Default,Fuu,0,0,0,,Are there any spells\Nto get me home quickly?
Dialogue: 50,0:20:33.13,0:20:34.30,Default,Fuu,0,0,0,,Or to make me fly?
Dialogue: 50,0:20:34.92,0:20:36.55,Default,Uguisu,0,0,0,,If you mess it up, you'll fall.
Dialogue: 50,0:20:36.55,0:20:38.55,Default,Fuu,0,0,0,,Whoa, that's no good!
Dialogue: 50,0:20:41.18,0:20:42.80,Default,Fuu,0,0,0,,I'm home!
Dialogue: 50,0:20:43.18,0:20:46.27,Default,Fuu,0,0,0,,Please let me keep them!
Dialogue: 50,0:20:46.27,0:20:49.77,Default,Fuu,0,0,0,,I'll do tons of chores\Nand finish all my homework!
Dialogue: 50,0:20:52.65,0:20:54.02,Default,Mom,0,0,0,,What do you think?
Dialogue: 50,0:20:54.02,0:20:56.69,Default,Dad,0,0,0,,They're funny-looking cats,\Nbut it seems fine to me.
Dialogue: 50,0:20:56.69,0:20:58.24,Default,Mom,0,0,0,,As long as you take care of them.
Dialogue: 50,0:20:58.24,0:21:00.78,Default,Fuu,0,0,0,,Thank you so much, Mom and Dad!
Dialogue: 50,0:21:01.28,0:21:03.16,Default,Dad,0,0,0,,What will you name them?
Dialogue: 50,0:21:07.50,0:21:09.87,Default,Fuu,0,0,0,,Azuki and Uguisu!
Dialogue: 50,0:21:12.88,0:21:14.13,Default,Dad,0,0,0,,Good choice.
Dialogue: 50,0:21:14.13,0:21:15.92,Default,Dad,0,0,0,,Oh yeah, did you see, Fuu?
Dialogue: 50,0:21:15.92,0:21:18.63,Default,Mom,0,0,0,,There were fireworks going off earlier.
Dialogue: 50,0:21:19.97,0:21:21.84,Default,Fuu,0,0,0,,Y-Yup, I saw them!
Dialogue: 50,0:21:22.30,0:21:23.60,Default,Fuu,0,0,0,,I'm gonna go change.
Dialogue: 50,0:21:30.60,0:21:32.98,Default,Fuu,0,0,0,,Wrong way, Azuki.
Dialogue: 50,0:21:35.19,0:21:36.07,Default,Rui,0,0,0,,What is it?
Dialogue: 50,0:21:38.36,0:21:39.53,Default,Fuu,0,0,0,,Big sis!
Dialogue: 50,0:21:39.99,0:21:43.11,Default,Fuu,0,0,0,,I took in these cats!
Dialogue: 50,0:21:43.11,0:21:44.53,Default,Rui,0,0,0,,I see!{そうなんだ}
Dialogue: 50,0:21:45.83,0:21:47.29,Default,Rui,0,0,0,,They're very cute.
Dialogue: 50,0:21:51.58,0:21:56.63,Default,Fuu,0,0,0,,There were these great big fireworks\Nin the sky earlier. Did you see them?
Dialogue: 50,0:21:59.67,0:22:00.34,Default,Rui,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 50,0:22:03.47,0:22:06.05,Default,Rui,0,0,0,,They were beautiful.
Dialogue: 50,0:22:19.61,0:22:22.11,Default,Fuu,0,0,0,,Things are about to get a lot more fun!{明日から "from tomorrow"}
